    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so excited to pass this beauty along to a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom-level shape\u2014it\u2019s basically like driving a brand-new car off the lot! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept in a garage, and it runs like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. You really have to see it in person to believe how gorgeous it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love for you to come take it for a spin! \u2728",
