    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its pre-owned status. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that is absolutely flawless; the paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. The interior is equally pristine, featuring premium leather surfaces that remain supple and uncreased, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every technological feature, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the intuitive navigation interface, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized service centers with all records available for review. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road wear. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
